headline: Why Target Tumbled 27% in the First Half of 2025
summary: It has contended with a boycott and weakness in discretionary spending.  To return to growth, the company has announced a multi-year acceleration program.  Target's (NYSE: TGT) troubles have continued thus far in 2025.

headline: A $100 billion mystery is unfolding on tariffs and inflation and economists are cracking the case
summary: The hottest question in economics is why the massive price hikes tariffs were supposed to bring still haven’t materialized halfway through 2025.
